.instructions.section
  %h2 Instructions

  %p CO 120 sts.
  %p pm and join for knitting in the round, taking care not to twist.

  %h3 Cable Set One
  - forest_park.instructions[:cable_set_one].each_with_index do |round, number|
    .row.flex.pad-bottom
      .number.cell-small
        %span Round #{number + 1}:
      .text.cell-large
        %span #{round}

  %p Repeat Rounds 1–4 6 times more (7 times total).

  %h3 Cable Set Two
  - forest_park.instructions[:cable_set_two].each_with_index do |round, number|
    .row.flex.pad-bottom
      .number.cell-small
        %span Round #{number + 1}:
      .text.cell-large
        %span #{round}
  %p Repeat Rounds 5–8 9 times more (10 times total).

  %h3 Finishing

  %p BO all sts and block gently.
  %p Pro tip: use beer, wine, or soda bottles to block the edges of your cowl to prevent unsightly fold marks.
